Design a network in CISCO packet tracer to connect ACCOUNTS and DELIVERY departments through the following:
a. Each department should contaion at least 2 PCs.
b. Appropriate number of switches and routers shaould be used in the network.
c. using the given network address 192.168.40.0, all interfaceshould be configured with appropriate IP adresses, subnet mask and gateways.
d. All devices in the network should be connected using appropriate cables.
e. Test thhe connectivity between ACCOUNTS and DELEVRY department- PCs in DELIVERY department should be able to ping the PCs in ACCOUNTS department.
